title: Budget 2026: High-powered standing committee will assess impact of emerging technologies including AI on jobs
description: Finance Minister Nirmala Sitharaman has announced a high-powered standing committee has been announced to assess the impact of emerging technologies, including artificial intelligence (AI), on employment. The committee will examine how new and emerging technologies are affecting jobs, with a specific focus on AI and its implications for the workforce.
